This test file covers `ValidateCreate` and `ValidateUpdate` for nil plugins, valid platforms, and duplicate architectures. It follows the existing test style in this package (table-driven `t.Run`, no Ginkgo — matching `clusterpodplacementconfig_types_test.go`).

